snippet.title: MEGA MAN X DiVE Offline - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
MEGA MAN X DiVE Offline is available now on Steam, iOS, and Android! DiVE into the world of Mega Man X and enjoy fast-paced classic side-scrolling action that lets you choose from more than 100 iconic playable characters across the Mega Man franchise.

Official Site: https://www.capcom-games.com/megaman/xdive-offline/en-us/
